<style>
    /* Defines gradient background and ensures text is centered */
    body {
        font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgb(255, 222, 173), rgb(173, 216, 230));
        margin: 0;
        padding-top: 80px;
        text-align: center;
        min-height: 100vh;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    /* Container for hover sliding navigation bar */
    .header-hover-area {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        z-index: 1000;
    }

    /* Animates and styles dropping navigation bar */
    .sliding-nav-container {
        width: 100%;
        background-color: rgb(255, 218, 185);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        padding: 10px 0;
        transform: translateY(0);
        transition: none;
    }

    /* Defines margins and text alignment for the navigation bar */
    .sliding-nav-container nav {
        margin: 5px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    /* Styles unhovered navigation links */
    .sliding-nav-container nav a {
        display: inline-block;
        margin: 0 20px;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: rgb(0, 102, 204);
        font-size: 2.5em;
        transition: color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    /* Transitions navigation links to different color when hovered */
    nav a:hover {
        color: rgb(255, 105, 180);
        transform: scale(1.1);
        text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* Enables the dropdown bar to... drop down */
    .header-hover-area:hover .sliding-nav-container {
        transform: translateY(0);
    }

    /* Defines main header "Welcome to EduPlay" */
    h1 {
        color: rgb(72, 61, 139);
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        font-size: 6em;
    }

    /* Formats home page description */
    .description {
        font-size: 1.5em;
        max-width: 80%;
        margin: 0 auto;
        text-align: center;
        color: rgb(75, 0, 130);
        background-color: rgb(255, 239, 213);
        border: 2px solid rgb(157, 189, 232);
        border-radius: 15px;
        padding: 15px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        max-width: 37.5em;
        transition: color .5s, transform .5s;
    }
    .description:hover {
        color: rgb(72, 34, 73);
        transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    /* For bottom playground image */
    .bottom-image {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 50%;
        border-radius: 20px;
        display: block;
        margin: 40px auto 20px auto;
    }
</style>


<h1>Welcome To EduPlay!</h1>

<body>
    <div class="header-hover-area">
        <div class="sliding-nav-container">
            <nav> 
                <a href="/games">Play Games</a>
                <a href="/videos">Watch Videos</a>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="description">
       EduPlay is a colorful, secure world where 2 to 7 year olds embark on joyful journeys through early math. 
        Here, children spark their curiosity with playful matching adventures recognizing numbers at their own pace, 
        while animated videos ensure that the children do their proper exercise. 
        Alongside with these exercises, our leaderboard celebrates every little victory, 
        motivating young learners to reach higher with each click. EduPlay turns screen time into a confidence-boosting environment, 
        where every game and video lays the foundation for the love of learning.
        
    </div>

    <img src="/playground.jpg" class="bottom-image" alt="Playground">
</body>
